<sect1 id="dir_544ce1c1aa4b1192c48075f8adda6aff_1autotoc_md447">
<title>UiTextBoundsUpdateSystem</title><para>Queries entities with <computeroutput>UiTextComponent</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>ModelAabbComponent</computeroutput>. When the text component signals <computeroutput>needsResize()</computeroutput>, the system retrieves the new AABB from the underlying <computeroutput>TextRenderable</computeroutput> and updates <computeroutput>ModelAabbComponent</computeroutput>.</para>
